PrecisOrder conferring general authority upon the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into (a) SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENTS with Indian Bands where the settlement being contemplated does not involve any land transactions and the monetary compensation does not exceed seven million dollars, and (b) Agreements with one or more provinces to facilitate the resolution of those claims.
